title: Getting Together A Twisted Tree Line Team Together For Rank Opening On Thursday
body: Anyone interested in getting together a team in twisted tree line, I am currently gold 2 with no effort this season and last season plat, hit me up if interested ( Doesn't matter what rank you are but how you play and game knowledge)
